(144, 'gamemonetize-33940', 'pale-pursuit', 'Pale Pursuit', 'https://img.gamemonetize.com/2ivlxn263ym6kgvgguy8r7qpgpztt4sx/512x384.jpg', '0', 4, 0, '0', 'Run fast, jump high, and don&amp;amp;rsquo;t look back in Pale Pursuit! Haunted by relentless ghostly figures, you must leap over enemy spirits and deadly traps to stay alive. The pace never slows and the phantoms never stop&amp;amp;mdash;only your reflexes can keep you ahead. Precision and timing are your only tools in this eerie, fast-paced survival chase. How long can you outrun the pale shadows of the night?', 'Click to jump', 'https://html5.gamemonetize.com/2ivlxn263ym6kgvgguy8r7qpgpztt4sx/', 'html5', 800, 600, 1748447446, '1', '0', 0, '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '[\"6\",\"156\",\"48\",\"218\"]', NULL, 0, NULL),
