(154, 'gamemonetize-33930', 'rogue-seas-adventure', 'Rogue Seas Adventure', 'https://img.gamemonetize.com/b7fi1enampkyavtm4pg1vi7v4kt1o5bl/512x384.jpg', '0', 11, 0, '0', 'Set sail with a fearless straw-hat kid and his rubber-quick reflexes in Rogue Seas Adventure! Hop between tiny islands, rescue captured crewmates, and stack your power before the final clash with the swampy sea-boss. Draw the perfect path, grab hidden treasure chests, and watch your elastic hero&amp;amp;rsquo;s strength skyrocket from 5 &amp;amp;rarr; 9 &amp;amp;rarr; &amp;amp;infin;&amp;amp;mdash;all in snappy, one-minute puzzle rounds. Dream of becoming the next great Pirate King? This is your first step. Gather your crew, sharpen your instincts, and rule the rogue seas!', 'Tap islands to add their numbers to yours mdash stack the biggest total and crush the boss', 'https://html5.gamemonetize.com/b7fi1enampkyavtm4pg1vi7v4kt1o5bl/', 'html5', 600, 960, 1748447446, '1', '0', 0, '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '[\"18\",\"73\",\"165\",\"3\",\"202\"]', NULL, 0, NULL),
